{"tid":1973411,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局宣布 DSE 4月24開考但有延期日子?","createTime":"2020-04-15T07:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T01:36:42.000Z","uid":310131,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cb6507119411c79285fa14f47c5f5ac4b5e07acb","tid":1973411,"uid":310131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:30:59.000Z","msg":"教育局長楊潤雄今午（15日）於記者會表示，中學文憑試（DSE）將於下周五（24日）如期開考，並於7月22日放榜。教育局亦因應新型冠狀病毒疫情擬定了兩個後備日期，分別為5月22日開考、8月中放榜，以及6月11日開考、8月底放榜。若6月11日仍未能開考，考試會取消。<br />\n<br />\n考生需備新舊准考證應試<br />\n<br />\n考評局稱，明日（16日）起會發出更新的准考證，考生需要帶備新舊兩張准考證應考，進入考場要戴口罩、量體溫及提交健康申報表。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">姐係點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日子都set好咗<br />\n係咪已經預咗延期<br />\n要等到最後個幾日先講呀?</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">玩撚完我地未呀?</span></span><br />\n我真係唔想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b6412cba3d2c6722c8d6a66b80c8b0341c646b","tid":1973411,"uid":355943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:31:50.000Z","msg":"食屎啦楊潤雄"},{"pid":"492c66f60cff40c1d231e0e4779699454699a703","tid":1973411,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:32:10.000Z","msg":"打算去到試埸先趕走你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e14a19ca56add3d000053f5c9947e674c3e4f3f","tid":1973411,"uid":244870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:35:06.000Z","msg":"繼續温書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a843264bb662ad3346f01aefb791ede3bd18de7d","tid":1973411,"uid":205339,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"cb6507119411c79285fa14f47c5f5ac4b5e07acb","tid":1973411,"uid":310131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-0