/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n究竟我地條命係乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔想死呀 我仲有大把野未做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b4bccabcbe1246b105cb9c1c0005c897cbd2b0","tid":1973411,"uid":310131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"44cd6bbc9f9a1ef5c6afb6422128f80faee22353","tid":1973411,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:42:27.000Z","msg":"咁你地係咪想23號單日1000個確診都照24號開考先？<br />\n考得DSE都成18歲諗嘢可唔可以成熟少少？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:51:00.000Z","msg":"唔係呀師姐<br />\n延期唔緊要,唔想搵命搏<br />\n我都係考個試姐。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用咁多時間去溫 邊個會想考完出黎自己瀨野..<br />\n所以我係覺得延期呢個做法冇問題。<br />\n但佢延期早啲通知 我會減少啲無畏嘅焦慮姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我真係好大壓力呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"eb8795ca037bcdd4f9c71bfeac5d17c9d79d1edd","tid":1973411,"uid":346084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:00:32.000Z","msg":"兩手準備啫 始終呢場疫症不可預測<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗咁多啦 專心溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f2d2807c0161330ed3f8c1feeb1d99ff1829c0","tid":1973411,"uid":54376,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:01:06.000Z","msg":"講真，今年呢班考生真係慘喎，呢個正苦垃撚圾又信唔過<br />\n疫情未完就話 24 號考，根本搵命搏<br />\n然後一路都冇明確後備方案，一出事就淨係識不斷延期，咁你想今年考 DSE 嗰班溫書溫幾耐先<br />\n屌你老味，又掟多兩個乜鳩擬定後備日子5月同 6月，真係人都癲"},{"pid":"114dedda9688f0de707b08add960b060d18e4191","tid":1973411,"uid":345524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T14:22:42.000Z","msg":"而家全世界度度都咁多uncertainty ，班仆街都話要照考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連大專大學都網上學習啦，究竟當班DSE考生係咩？制度上嘅一堆棋子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，成班食屎狗，狗都不如添呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf2ed8b35ba9a209b71e4e9bc9d82a468777d727","tid":1973411,"uid":200210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T01:36:42.000Z","msg":"直接取消好過啦<br />\n取消佢最冇隱憂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}